":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"19e047d84ce0fdae4af14331ac7b62fb4beb1cab","tid":2373634,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"含啦問問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4ba94e631060fe4a89d0dde0e60b15856b8358","tid":2373634,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"球員是不是在越位位置上，由兩個條件決定，即球的位置及對方站在最後第二位的球員位置（註：因為對方陣營之最後位置的球員「通常」是龍門，所以越位線其中一個條件必然是對方站在最後第二位的球員位置）。當球員所在的位置比「球和站在最後第二位的對方球員更靠近對方底線」，就處於越位位置。但若此球員處於本方半場內，則不受此限制。如果球員和第二名對方球員平行，亦不算越位。"},{"pid":"4b99692230ebfc86cea30d01bbfb5377f03e65bf","tid":2373634,"uid":100882,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"之前睇到熊仔頭有個解釋幾好<br />\n因為個球員跑得太快，旁證怕佢攰所以叫停佢，等佢做個「穴位」按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce5af765777cfc6bdbdad37ab927d6ae770aa3a","tid":2373634,"uid":99700,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"4b99692230ebfc86cea30d01bbfb5377f03e65bf","tid":2373634,"uid":100882,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"之前睇到熊仔頭有個解釋幾好<br />\n因為個球員跑得太快，旁證怕佢攰所以叫停佢，等佢做個「穴位」按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"石頭出糧"},{"pid":"6bdebb989f3cfe32fc5f7a12743ed6cccc72bd78","tid":2373634,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"球證話有就有"},{"pid":"080aafb81f885e85c6a8eb5c02c98bd12dc4fcf6","tid":2373634,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T19:41:39.000Z","msg":"你唔俾屌但條撚仍然插入左你個西"},{"pid":"be6ec25b96d1de8b0c62bfebce977081e9ea4ea3","tid":2373634,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4ba94e631060fe4a89d0dde0e60b15856b8358","tid":2373634,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"cite